      "title": "11-Hour water cut on Saturday (30)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); National Water Supply and Drainage Board announced that there will be an 11-hour water cut for Colombo 9, 10, 11, and 12 from 9 PM on Saturday (30) to 8 AM on Sunday (31).",
